operations.name: Emergency Outage Dispatch Report
operations.description: This is a version of the "Jobs with Upcoming Appointments" report specifically filtered to be used to dispatch technicians in an emergency where you do not have access to ServiceTitan. Schedule this report to be emailed to you at least once daily (but no more than hourly). The more frequently you have it sent, the more up-to-date data you'll have in an outage scenario. When scheduling, choose "flexible report", set the "filter by" field to "Jobs with Next Appt Start Date" and set the date range to "Today". Other fields are up to your discretion.  We recommend creating a filter in your email client to keep these from cluttering your inbox.

operations.name: Incorrect Deferred Revenue Billing Templates
operations.description: This report will show a list of customer membership records that incorrectly have a task that sells or renews a membership on a billing template which will prevent users from passing a TitanAdvisor checkpoint. If a customer membership record appears on this report, that means that the task has a workflow action that either sells or renews a membership and needs to be changed to a task that does not have these workflow actions.

operations.name: Incorrect GL Setup for Recurring Services
operations.description: This report will return a list of recurring service invoice template items that are are not tied to the correct GL account type for membership types that are set up for deferred revenue which will prevent users from passing a TitanAdvisor checkpoint. For deferred revenue setup, the negative item on the template should be tied to a liability GL account type and the positive item should be tied to an income GL account type. These 2 items should be equal in value, where one is positive and one is negative. If a recurring service template invoice item is on this report, the GL account should be changed to reflect the correct setup.

operations.name: Incorrect Location Recurring Services Marked as First Visit Complete
operations.description: This report will return a list of location recurring services where "First Visit Complete" checkbox is checked on memberships that are setup for deferred revenue which will prevent users from passing a TitanAdvisor checkpoint. The "First Visit Complete" checkbox should not be checked on location recurring services if using deferred revenue because it will cause reporting to be incorrect. Location Recurring Services that appear on this report need to have that checkbox unchecked.

technician.name: Field Conversion Report
technician.description: This report should be used to evaluate technician performance around conversions. This report includes the SLM conversion rate, which is especially useful in evaluating a technician as it counts the job as converted if they set a lead, sell a membership or convert the job. If you are looking for a conversion rate that accounts for leads set, this is a great calculation. This report also includes other helpful KPIs such as options per opportunity, billable hours, and basic conversion metrics.

technician.name: Field Quality Report
technician.description: This report should be used to get quick insight into the quality of work the technician is doing. This will include counts on many job classifications such as warranty and recall. The report also shows revenue before and after adjustment invoices.

technician.name: Sales Report by Field Employee/Technician
technician.description: This report is used to focus on conversion of estimates. This report is best used to evaluate how effective your field employee is at converting an estimate, independent of whether or not work was performed that day. This would be a great report to use to evaluate performance if a field employee is focused on selling.

technician.name: Sold By Sales Detail Report by Completion Date
technician.description: Upgrade to legacy Sold By Sales Detail Report by Completion Date. Displays invoice details of completed jobs, based on the Sold By technician. Use this to evaluate the work generated by your salesmen that has been completed.
